man rifle]]s'''\n|- \n| [[File:Galil-Sniper-Galatz-r001.jpg|centre|120px]] || [[IMI Galil#Galil Sniper|IMI Galatz]] ||[[Sniper rifle]] || [[7.62\u00d751mm NATO]] || {{Flagu|Israel}} || Used in small numbers.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chaoprayanews.com/blog/yotin/2014/07/29/imi-galil-%E0%B8%82%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%94-5-56-mm-%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A5%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%88%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%A3/|title=IMI GALIL \u0e02\u0e19\u0e32\u0e14 5.56 mm \u0e1b\u0e37\u0e19\u0e40\u0e25\u0e47\u0e01\u0e01\u0e25\u0e08\u0e32\u0e01\u0e2d\u0e34\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e32\u0e40\u0e2d\u0e25\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e43\u0e0a\u0e49\u0e43\u0e19\u0e23\u0e32\u0e0a\u0e01\u0e32\u0e23\u0e01\u0e23\u0e21\u0e23\u0e32\u0e0a\u0e17\u0e31\u0e13\u0e11\u0e4c \u0e41\u0e25\u0e30 \u0e02\u0e19\u0e32\u0e14 7.62 mm \u0e1b\u0e37\u0e19\u0e0b\u0e38\u0e48\u0e21\u0e22\u0e34\u0e07\u0e02\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e01\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e17\u0e31\u0e1e\u0e1a\u0e01|work=chaoprayanews.com|access-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725081229/http://chaoprayanews.com/blog/yotin/2014/07/29/imi-galil-%E0%B8%82%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%94-5-56-mm-%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A5%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%88%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%A3|archive-date=2017-07-25|url-status=dead|df=}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:SIG Sauer SSG 3000.jpg|centre|120px]] || [[SIG Sauer SSG 3000]] || Sniper rifle || 7.62\u00d751mm NATO || {{Flagu|Switzerland}} ||<ref name=\"mfa\">{{cite web|url=http://www.militaryfactory.com/smallarms/detail.asp?smallarms_id=817|title=SIG-Sauer SSG 3000 Bolt-Action Sniper Rifle - Switzerland|publisher=|access-date=19 November 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129033420/http://www.militaryfactory.com/smallarms/detail.asp?smallarms_id=817|archive-date=29 November 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:MSG 90 rifle 2014 noBG.jpg|centre|120px]] || [[Heckler & Koch PSG1#MSG90|Heckler and