en 68.jpg|centre|120px]] || [[Type 84|Type 84 AVLB]] || [[Armoured vehicle-launched bridge]] || {{Flagu|China}} || 4 in Service.<ref name=srrphawuth /> Based on the Type 69 MBT. 18 m long mobile bridge. \n|-\n! style=\"align: centre; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | '''Support equipments'''\n|-\n| [[File:Bailey bridge element, Ranville 01 09.jpg|centre|120px]] ||[[Bailey bridge]] || [[Bridge|Man portable bridge]] || {{Flagu|UK}} || <ref>{{Cite web|title=\u0e17\u0e2b\u0e32\u0e23\u0e1a\u0e01\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e49\u0e32\u0e07\u0e2a\u0e30\u0e1e\u0e32\u0e19\u0e40\u0e1a\u0e25\u0e25\u0e35\u0e48 \u0e43\u0e2b\u0e49\u0e04\u0e19\u0e40\u0e14\u0e34\u0e19\u0e02\u0e49\u0e32\u0e21\u0e04\u0e25\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e2d\u0e14\u0e40\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e47\u0e08\u0e41\u0e25\u0e49\u0e27|url= https://www.matichon.co.th/politics/news_331192|website=www.matichon.co.th|first=matichon |last=Online|date=30 June 2015|accessdate=22 October 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:DF-ST-85-04824 An M60A3 main battle tank crosses a medium girder bridge during Exercise REFORGER '83.jpeg |centre|120px]] ||[[Medium Girder Bridge]] ||[[Bridge|Man portable bridge]] ||{{Flagu|UK}} || <ref name=\"\u0e14\u0e39\u0e07\u0e32\u0e19 \u0e01\u0e23\u0e21\u0e01\u0e32\u0e23\u0e17\u0e2b\u0e32\u0e23\u0e0a\u0e48\u0e32\u0e07...\"/>\n|}\n\n====Support engineering vehicles====\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:9%;\"| Photo\n! style=\"width:15%;\"| Model\n! style=\"width:15%;\"| Type\n! style=\"width:15%;\"| Origin\n! Notes\n|-\n! style=\"align: centre; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | '''Support engineering vehicles'''\n|-\n| [[File:JASDF Excavator(Kobelco, 44-7013) at Tsuiki Air Base November 26, 2017 04.jpg|centre|120px]] || [[Volvo]] [[Excavator]] || [[Excavator]] || {{Flagu|Sweden}} ||<ref name=EngineerUnits>{{Cite web|title=Engineer Unit ,Royal Thai Army :Assessment and Advisory Visit|url= https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q0Ojn4Kb9L0|website=www.youtube.com|first=Burin|last=Teerawattanavisi